  "notebookEntry": {
    "content": "<h2>Výkon</h2>\n<p><strong>Výkon</strong> vyjadřuje, jak rychle se koná práce (jaká práce se vykoná za jednotku času).</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 400 120' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <rect x='30' y='20' width='140' height='80' rx='10' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <text x='100' y='50' text-anchor='middle' fill='#1e40af' font-size='16' font-weight='bold'>W [J]</text>\n  <text x='100' y='75' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>práce</text>\n  <rect x='230' y='20' width='140' height='80' rx='10' fill='#f0fdf4' stroke='#22c55e' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <text x='300' y='50' text-anchor='middle' fill='#166534' font-size='16' font-weight='bold'>t [s]</text>\n  <text x='300' y='75' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>čas</text>\n  <line x1='170' y1='60' x2='230' y2='60' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <text x='200' y='55' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='16'>÷</text>\n  <text x='200' y='115' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='16' font-weight='bold'>P = W / t [W]</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Vzorec</h3>\n<div class='formula'>$$P = \\frac{W}{t}$$</div>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Veličina</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Jednotka</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>výkon</td><td>P</td><td>W (watt)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>práce</td><td>W</td><td>J</td></tr>\n<tr><td>čas</td><td>t</td><td>s</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Jednotky výkonu</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Jednotka</th><th>Převod</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>1 W</td><td>1 J/s</td></tr>\n<tr><td>1 kW</td><td>1 000 W</td></tr>\n<tr><td>1 MW</td><td>1 000 000 W</td></tr>\n<tr><td>1 k (kůň)</td><td>≈ 735 W</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Příklad</h3>\n<p>Jeřáb zvedne náklad o hmotnosti 500 kg do výšky 12 m za 20 s. Jaký je výkon?</p>\n<div class='formula'>$$W = F \\cdot s = m \\cdot g \\cdot h = 500 \\cdot 10 \\cdot 12 = 60\\,000 \\, \\text{J}$$</div>\n<div class='formula'>$$P = \\frac{W}{t} = \\frac{60\\,000}{20} = 3\\,000 \\, \\text{W} = 3 \\, \\text{kW}$$</div>"
  }
}
